HEADWORD: Volutation
<hw>Vol`u*ta"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>volutatio</ets>, from <ets>volutare</ets> to roll, wallow, verb
freq. <ets>volvere</ets>, <ets>volutum</ets>, to roll.]</ety> <def>A
